---
import LegalPage from "../../components/LegalPage.astro";
import { getLocalizedPath } from "../../i18n/site";

const locale = "en";
const updatedAt = "March 17, 2026";
const pageDescription =
  "This page sets out the terms and conditions under which the ISAF S.A. website may be used, as well as the rules applicable to the content published online.";
---

<LegalPage
  locale={locale}
  currentPage="terms"
  title="Terms and Conditions"
  description={pageDescription}
  updatedAt={updatedAt}
>
  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 sm:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">1. Website operator details</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        The website is operated by <strong>ISAF S.A.</strong>, with correspondence address at
        68 Lugoj Street, P.O. Box 012212, District 1, Bucharest, Romania, registered under
        <strong> VAT No.: 473734</strong> and <strong>Trade Register No.: J40/1079/1991</strong>.
      </p>
      <p>
        For additional information you may contact us at
        <a href="mailto:office@isaf.ro" class="text-red-400 hover:text-red-300"> office@isaf.ro</a> or at
        <a href="tel:+40212208075" class="text-red-400 hover:text-red-300"> +40 21 220 80 75</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 sm:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">2. Acceptance of the terms</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        By accessing and using this website, you confirm that you have read, understood, and accepted these terms of use.
        If you do not agree with these provisions, please do not use the website.
      </p>
      <p>
        ISAF S.A. may periodically update the content of this page. Continued use of the website after publication of
        changes constitutes acceptance of the updated version.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 sm:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">3. Purpose of the website</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        The website is intended for presentation and information purposes and is designed to publish information about
        the company, products, activity areas, and contact methods.
      </p>
      <p>
        Information displayed on the website does not constitute, in the absence of express confirmation from ISAF S.A.,
        a binding offer, contractual commitment, or warranty regarding the availability of products, services, technical
        specifications, delivery deadlines, or commercial conditions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 sm:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">4. Permitted use of content</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Users may access the website only for legitimate informational and commercial purposes compatible with its nature.
        It is prohibited to use the website in a manner that:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>violates the law, public order, or the rights of others;</li>
        <li>affects the security, availability, or functioning of the website;</li>
        <li>introduces malicious code, attempts unauthorized access, abusive scraping, or other similar actions;</li>
        <li>reproduces, distributes, or exploits the website content outside the limits permitted by law or without the rights holder's consent.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 sm:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">5. Intellectual property</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        The content of the website, including without limitation the texts, images, graphic elements, logos, structure,
        design, and published materials, belongs to ISAF S.A. and/or its partners, as applicable, and is protected by
        applicable intellectual property laws.
      </p>
      <p>
        Viewing and using the content is permitted solely for personal information purposes. Any copying, republication,
        adaptation, distribution, or commercial use of the content requires the prior written consent of the rights holder,
        except where expressly permitted by law.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 sm:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">6. Contact form and communications</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        By sending a request through the contact form or by email, you confirm that the information provided is accurate
        and that you have the right to communicate it.
      </p>
      <p>
        Use of the form for false, abusive, defamatory, unlawful, misleading messages or for sending unsolicited materials is prohibited.
      </p>
      <p>
        The way we process personal data communicated through the form is described in the
        <a href={getLocalizedPath(locale, "privacy")} class="text-red-400 hover:text-red-300"> Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 sm:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">7. Accuracy of information</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        ISAF S.A. makes reasonable efforts to ensure that the published information is accurate and up to date.
        However, we do not guarantee that all information on the website is complete, current, or error-free at all times.
      </p>
      <p>
        Direct communication with company representatives is required to confirm technical characteristics, availability,
        and commercial conditions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 sm:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">8. Limitation of liability</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        To the extent permitted by law, ISAF S.A. is not liable for indirect, special, or consequential damages arising
        from the use or inability to use the website, interruptions, temporary unavailability, technical errors, or
        reliance placed solely on information published online.
      </p>
      <p>
        Nothing in this section limits liability that cannot be excluded or limited under applicable law.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 sm:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">9. Links to third parties</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        The website may contain links to external websites or services. They are provided solely for information
        or to facilitate contact and do not imply approval of the content or responsibility for the practices of those operators.
      </p>
      <p>
        Use of third-party websites is at your own risk and subject to the terms established by those operators.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 sm:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">10. Governing law</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        These terms of use are governed by Romanian law. Any dispute arising from or in connection with the use of the
        website shall be settled by the competent courts in Romania, unless the law provides otherwise.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.03] p-6 sm:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">11. Contact</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        For questions regarding these terms of use, you may write to us at
        <a href="mailto:office@isaf.ro" class="text-red-400 hover:text-red-300"> office@isaf.ro</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</LegalPage>
